ompare and synthesize data sets from multiple exoplanet\ndetection techniques in order to infer exoplanet demographics over wider\nregions of parameter space than are accessible to individual methods. In a\ncompanion paper, we apply our methodology to several representative\nmicrolensing and RV surveys to derive the frequency of planets around M dwarfs\nwith orbits of $\\lesssim 30~$years.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Apr 2014 20:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
